Usage: hdiutil pmap [options] <image|device>
	pmap options:
	    -simple       - MediaKit's minimal report
	    -standard     - MediaKit's standard report (no free space)
	    -complete     - MK's comprehensive report (w/end offsets)
	    -diagnostic   - MK's diagnostic mode (display all schemes)

	    -endoffsets   - indicate last block of each partition
	    -nofreespace  - don't show free space
	    -shims        - show small islands of space < 32 blocks
	    -uuids        - show uuid of gpt partitions

	The default behaviour shows all partitions and free space.

	Common options:
	    -shadow <shadowfile>
	    -insecurehttp
	    -cacert <file | dir>
	    -verbose
	    -debug
	    -quiet
